
Requirements
------------

You must have the Subversion command line application, svn, installed.

How to Use
----------

Add big-brother/bin to your path.  On Windows, use big-brother.bat even if you're using Cygwin (or fix the shell script).

$ big-brother --help

Subversion only

$ big-brother -s https://alm.pervasive.com/svn/master -c syoung wnavey echun -u scox --pp pcc.core di.services

Subversion and Sonar

$ big-brother -s https://alm.pervasive.com/svn/master -S https://alm.pervasive.com/sonar -c syoung wnavey echun -u scox --pp pcc.core di.services
